b.archive.org/web/20100611070713/http://www.esmas.com/vanguardialatina/comunidadvl/724696.html EspacioUSA Vanguardia Latina]\n| [https://books.google.com/books?id=CoI5x69D4KkC&pg=PA237&dq=Rafael+Fern%C3%A1ndez+de+Castro&client=firefox-a#PPA237,M1 Migration Issues: Raising the Stakes in U.S.-Latin American Relations]\n[https://books.google.com/books?id=ipdE0cVFECgC&pg=PR4&dq=Rafael+Fern%C3%A1ndez+de+Castro&client=firefox-a The United States and Mexico]\n|-\n![[Heidi Cruz]]\n!Regional head of the Southwest United States for Goldman Sachs' Investment Management Division, [[Goldman Sachs]], Houston Texas\n!\n|-\n| [[Ram\u00f3n Garza|Ram\u00f3n Alberto Garza]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Gordon Giffin|Gordon D. Giffin]]\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20100917163043/http://americanambassadors.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=Members.view&memberid=284 Council of American Ambassadors]\n[http://www.mckennalong.com/people-438.html McKenna Long & Aldridge]\n[https://people.forbes.com/profile/gordon-d-giffin/569 Forbes]\n| \n|-\n| [[Allan Gotlieb]]\n| [http://globetrotter.berkeley.edu/conversations/Gotlieb/ Institute of International Studies, UC Berkeley]\n[https://web.archive.org/web/20061114022055/http://www.trilateral.org/membship/bios/ag.htm Trilateral Commission]\n| [https://books.google.com/books?as_auth=Allan+Gotlieb&source=an&ei=vY6OSeGqNYmQtQP1mMSCCQ&sa=X&oi=book_group&resnum=4&ct=title&cad=author-navigational Book list]\n|-\n| Michael Hart\n| [https://carleton.ca/npsia/npsia_faculty/hart.html Norman Paterson School of International Affairs at Carleton University]\n[https://carleton.ca/npsia/npsia_faculty/pdf/Hart.pdf Academic resume]\n| \n|-\n| [[Carlos Heredia]]\n| [http://www.wilsoncenter.org/index.cfm?topic_id=5949&fuseaction=topics.item&news_id=477973 Woodrow International Center for Scholars]\n| \n|-\n| [[Carla A. Hills]]\n| [http://www.cfr.org/bios/3373/carla_a_hills.html Council on Foreign Relations]\n[https://web.archive.org/web/20090610092406/http://www.csis.org/component/opti